c: 3
v: 19
t: "Inene inkolo (eyamkelekileyo) kuAllâh yi-Islam. Abo babenikwe isiBhalo (amaYuda namaKhristu) azanga babe neyantlukwano, ngaphandle kokumonelana, emva kokuba ulwazi lwalusele lufikile kubo. Nabani na ongakholwayo kwiiVesi zika-Allâh, inene uAllâh Uyakhawuleza ukufaka (umntu) embuzweni"